OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Rob McElhenney make
OL,4,Canother business move in Wrexham
OL,6,FHollywood duo Ryan Reynolds and Rob
OL,7,FMcElhenney have been announced as the
OL,8,Fnew co-owners of a beer company in
OL,9,Ftheir new business venture in Wales.
OL,11,FWrexham Lager Beer Co. Ltd is the
OL,12,Foldest lager brewery still existing in
OL,13,FGreat Britain that has been brewing in
OL,14,FWales since 1882.
OL,16,FIt announced Rob McElhenney and Ryan
OL,17,FReynolds as new co-owners of the
OL,18,Fcompany alongside the Roberts family.
