OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Rob McElhenney make
OL,4,Canother business move in Wrexham
OL,6,FThe acquisition was made by Red Dragon
OL,7,FVentures, a joint venture formed by
OL,8,FThe R.R. McReynolds Company, majority
OL,9,Fowner of Wrexham AFC, and the Allyn
OL,10,Ffamily of Skaneateles, New York.
OL,12,FRed Dragon Ventures was created to
OL,13,Fdrive growth in the Wrexham community
OL,14,Fand Wrexham AFC.
OL,16,FDeadpool star Reynolds posted on X,
OL,17,Fformerly Twitter: "Took this whole
OL,18,F'Hold my beer' thing to its logical
OL,19,Fconclusion. Welcome to Wrexham Lager."
