OL,6,FThis transaction represents another
OL,7,Flandmark deal for the Welsh town.
OL,9,FRob McElhenney and Ryan Reynolds said:
OL,10,F"As co-chairmen of Wrexham AFC we have
OL,11,Flearned a lot. The connection between
OL,12,Fclub and community, the intricacies of
OL,13,Fthe offsides rule and the occasional
OL,14,Fneed for beer ` especially after
OL,15,Ffinance meetings.
OL,17,F"Wrexham Lager has a 140-year-old
OL,18,Frecipe and a storied history and we're
OL,19,Fexcited to help write its next
OL,20,Fchapter."
