OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Rob McElhenney make
OL,4,Canother business move in Wrexham
OL,6,FThe New York-based Allyn family were
OL,7,Fthe owners of US medical device
OL,8,Fmanufacturing company Welch Allyn Inc.
OL,9,FThat was until September 2015 when the
OL,10,Ffirm was sold to Hill-Rom in a deal
OL,11,Fworth more than $2bn. Since selling
OL,12,Fthe company, the family have turned
OL,13,Ftheir focus to investing in private
OL,14,Fand public markets, and are also noted
OL,15,Ffor their philanthropy.
OL,17,FRecently-appointed CEO James Wright
OL,18,Fhas continued to lead the business
OL,19,Fafter already overseeing rapid UK
OL,20,Fgrowth.
