OL,3,CRyan Reynolds and Rob McElhenney make
OL,4,Canother business move in Wrexham
OL,6,FHe said: "This is a brand with great
OL,7,Fheritage ` the oldest lager brewery in
OL,8,FGreat Britain, once enjoyed across the
OL,9,Fworld," said James Wright, CEO of the
OL,10,FWrexham Lager Beer Co. Ltd.
OL,12,F"So, to have Rob and Ryan onboard as
OL,13,Fwe embark on international expansion
OL,14,Fis huge for us. They have been doing
OL,15,Fwonders for the town of Wrexham and
OL,16,Fstrongly share our passion for once
OL,17,Fagain seeing Wrexham Lager enjoyed in
OL,18,Fall the far-flung corners of the
OL,19,Fglobe."
